452
00:32:33,017 --> 00:32:35,451
It's an addendum to
the witness list. Who?

453
00:32:35,520 --> 00:32:37,511
Dr. Elizabeth Olivet.

454
00:32:39,857 --> 00:32:43,452
<i>When you meet someone for the first
