certainty whether Mr. Duvall could have made a connection...

477
00:34:06,010 --> 00:34:09,605
<i>between Miss Zergin and his first
sexual experiences with his nanny?</i>

478
00:34:09,680 --> 00:34:11,113
It's possible.

479
00:34:13,751 --> 00:34:15,742
Thank you.

480
00:34:17,789 --> 00:34:21,691
There's no genetic marker for
A.S., is there? That's correct.

481
00:34:21,759 --> 00:34:26,389
No physiological evidence one can point to
that indicates someone has it? That's right.

482
00:34:26,464 --> 00:34:30,423
No blood test you could
run, no brain scan? No.

483
00:34:30,501 --> 00:34:33,664
Could a person fake the symptoms of A. S?

484
00:34:33,738 --> 00:34:36,935
<i>I'd like to think
