a mother's side of the story.

495
00:35:14,445 --> 00:35:18,313
Gabriel, dear, why don't you see if
Mrs. Judson can make you something?

496
00:35:18,382 --> 00:35:20,316
No, I think I'll stay.

497
00:35:21,953 --> 00:35:24,478
If I have to, Eleanor,
I'll subpoena you.

498
00:35:24,555 --> 00:35:27,422
