504
00:35:54,652 --> 00:35:56,984
And he's still in the room.

505
00:35:58,055 --> 00:36:00,114
Stop talking around me.

506
00:36:12,503 --> 00:36:17,531
I repeat, I have been forced to be here
against my will. I'll ask the question again.

507
00:36:17,608 --> 00:36:21,169
When did you first notice
that your son was different?

508
00:36:21,245 --> 00:36:25,011
Well, I don't know what you mean.
All children are different.

509
00:36:25,082 --> 00:36:28,711
<i>Isn't it a fact that Gabriel
has always had difficulties socially?</i>

510
00:36:28,786 --> 00:36:32,916
Gabriel was and is a perfect son.

511
00:36:32,990 --> 00:36:35,754
I have nothing else to say.

512
00:36:35,826 --> 00:36:39,284
<i>So you never saw any signs
of abnormal behavior?</i>

513
00:36:40,364 --> 00:36:43,231
