That's what makes us unique.

514
00:36:44,569 --> 00:36:47,265
Did you ever take Gabriel
to a specialist? Certainly.

515
00:36:47,338 --> 00:36:51,104
One said it was
marginal cerebral palsy,

516
00:36:51,175 --> 00:36:54,042
another thought
